config:
  name: "TinySkies Flight Controller"
  id: "tinyskies.flightController"
  author: "script-wizard"
  isScript: true
  main: "script.js"
  version: "1.0.0"
  description: "Quaternion-based plane physics on a globe. Verbatim port of source Plane.ts.update() (REQ-003..REQ-006), MVP-pruned of gremlin/boost/HP fields."
  documentation: "Reads keyboard (A/D yaw, W forward, S brake, ArrowUp climb, Space paintball) and integrates the source's exact spherical-flight state (qPosition, heading, pitch, bankAngle, speed, altitude). Writes the buildPlaneMatrix(...) result directly to gameObject._internal.three.matrix each frame (matrixAutoUpdate=false set by tinyskiesBiplaneVisual). Spins the propeller surfaced via parent.userData.tinyskiesPropeller. Publishes state to this.erth.store under 'tinyskies/*' keys for the camera rig and paintball system."
  tags:
