  documentation: "Tracks 7 hearts on the globe. Each cycles between active (visible, collectable) and pending-respawn (hidden, ticking down a 2-4s timer). On player proximity within COLLECT_RADIUS=0.3, heart deactivates and writes `tinyskies/applyHeartHeal` to the store with the heal amount (default HEAL_HP=3). The flightController consumes this signal in update() and adds to player HP. Source uses ShaderMaterial with hologram vert/frag; we use a TSL holographic colorNode (fresnel + sin-band hue cycle + emissive). Source's PointLight per heart preserved at intensity 0.38."
