  documentation: "Reads landmark normals from four published store keys: hotsprings (biomeDecor), shrines (landmarks), mushrooms (vegetation), butterflies (biomeDecor). Active only while vehicleType==='carpet'. Decay rate 0.3, fill rate 1/1.5 (0.667/s), enter dot 0.995 — verbatim from source. On completion, marks the site done in-memory (cross-session persistence will arrive with the Game Services pass), publishes `tinyskies/awardXp` (default 40 = LANDMARK_SELFIE_XP), and writes `tinyskies/selfieTaken` with {kind, kindIndex} for any progression listener."
