  documentation: "Verbatim port of source Rings.ts plane-mode subset (boat / carpet modes deferred — those need terrain). Geometry: OctahedronGeometry(0.09, 0) scaled (1, 1.5, 1) — same as source createPlaneCollectibleDiamondGeometry. Spawn placement: deterministic via seed; HIGH_ALTITUDE 35% chance, otherwise LOW_ALTITUDE. Each diamond bobs along its surface-radial + spins around it. Source ShaderMaterial holographic-rainbow → MeshBasicNodeMaterial + TSL fresnel hue shift (visually similar). On collection (planePos within COLLECTION_RADIUS 0.3), publishes `tinyskies/triggerBoost = true` (the flight controller reads-and-clears) and starts the diamond's respawn timer."
