  description: "Inland biome decorations on the deformed globe — 4 hot springs and 4 butterfly flower gardens with 36-52 procedural flowers each. Flowers are rendered through InstancedMesh buckets for stalks, centers, and petal colors. Steam and butterfly particles use three.quarks."
  documentation: "Two biome-niche systems on flat inland sites. Source seeds: 16161+seed (hotsprings), 223344+seed (butterfly gardens). Hotsprings use imported GLB templates when available and fall back to the procedural pool helper. Butterfly gardens preserve the source stalk + center + 5-petal flower structure and 6 pastel petal palettes, but batch repeated submeshes into InstancedMesh buckets to avoid hundreds of decorative draw calls."
