  priority: 0
  description: "Direct Three.js port of Bruno Simon's webgl-black-hole demo:
    50k disc particles + 50k star particles + cylindrical accretion disc +
    radial distortion mask, composed in a 2-pass renderer (space target +
    distortion target) and applied via a screen-aligned final quad parented
